ANZSCO 411 健康和福利人员 HEALTH AND WELFARE SUPPORT WORKERS - FLYabroad
ANZSCO 411 健康和福利人员职责概述 - FLYabroad
 协助健康专业人士对医院、疗养院、其他健康和基于社区的看护所的病人进行护理，就社会福利事情提供建议和信息。HEALTH AND WELFARE SUPPORT WORKERS assist Health Professionals in the provision of patient care in hospitals, nursing homes and other health and community-based care facilities, and provide support, information and advice to clients on a range of social welfare matters.
